{ It was about time to complete developing and bring the king to safety.  This could be done by   12...Bd6 !  as Black will answer  13.d5  with  exd5  14.exd5  Qe7+  15.Be2  Na5  16.Qa4+  Kd8 !  and now White's king will also face trouble in trying to leave the center. ...Re8 is threatened and therefore  17.Kf1  is forced. }
